articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents: This website was built by Hannah Koenker, Technical Director at Tropical Health. Both Stata and R were used for analysis and presentation of the findings. This website uses Distill.

articles.title: Textile Reports
articles.description: Does net textile affect net use?
articles.contents: This website provides reports for countries in sub-Saharan Africa to evaluate whether there are differences in use of insecticide-treated nets (ITNs) due to the textile of ITNs (i.e.Â polyester or polyethylene).
